column5: Yep. I'm 30 minutes away from Melbourne the "most liveable city on earth" and it's still fucking terrible.
I hope UBI comes into effect, that would really make shit easier because I don't want to work. My dream is travelling the country by bike until I run out of money then kill myself.

My dad belives crazy shit like this. He thinks the human race was created by superior beings who used us as slaves to make things like the pyramids and all those ancient mega structures. 

Thank god I will never have a child write my ridiculous delusional thoughts on the internet.
No being a prostitute isn't being neet. Neet is  unemployed, not in school and not in training.
15, haven't missed any f2p quests or tokens
Congrats on not being a fucking dickhead
Could be a possibility, I guess it just depends on how much money I have in the future. Making money online seems ridiculously hard and competitive though.
I'm 21 and heard "you look 12" every single fucking day. I fucking hate it, people take me as a joke and seriously if I look 13 at 21 then I am a fucking joke.
When my parents die I'm going to buy a bike and travel until I run out of money then rope

I saw it too on omegle when I was young. I didnt believe that it was possible or real for that to be on the internet but the 2 seconds i saw still haunts me 6/7+ years later.  I reported it but threw away the email, this thread seriously fucks me up and its been so many years. Years after seeing it i found out my mum was abused as a young child too. Makes me feel so sick and helpless and i hate that it happens all over the world 

I still feel guilt as well, i wish that shit was erased from my mind
